query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS leg_volumes (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  distributorId INT NOT NULL,
  periodStart DATE NOT NULL,
  periodEnd DATE NOT NULL,
  leftLegVolume INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  rightLegVolume INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  leftLegPv INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  rightLegPv INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  carryForwardLeft INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  carryForwardRight INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  binaryCommissionPaid INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_distributorId (distributorId),
  INDEX idx_periodStart (periodStart)
)
